SubjectCommission do issue under the Great Seal of Canada.
PrecisOrder directing that a COMMISSION do issue under the Great Seal of Canada empowering JURICA ČAPKUN to administer the Oath of Allegiance, the Oath of Office or any other oath as may from time to time be prescribed by law during his tenure of office as Assistant Clerk of the Queen’s Privy Council for Canada (Orders in Council).
